txt.en: You have defeated the Orc look-outs at the Harlond.
Orc look-outs placed at key locations throughout the Harlond should be dealt with quickly.
You have defeated a number of the Orc look-outs in the Harlond, reducing their ability to see attacks and spy targets within Lossarnach.
Orc look-outs are perched at many high spots around the Harlond, especially near the entrance, in the northmost part of Lossarnach.\n\nYou should dispatch a good number of Orc look-outs.

You have noticed many Orc look-outs placed at key locations throughout the Harlond. Defeating them would blind the Orcs to further attacks and reduce the chances to discover more targets in Lossarnach.
Orc look-outs are perched at many high spots around the Harlond, especially near the entrance, in the northmost part of Lossarnach.\n\nYou should dispatch a good number of Orc look-outs.
